<%#
# LazyHasMany Index Partial

This partial renders a has_many relationship,
to be displayed on a resource's index page.

By default, the relationship is rendered as a link to the associated object.

## Local variables:

- `field`:
  An instance of [Administrate::Field::LazyHasMany][1].
  A wrapper around the [Administrate::Field::HasMany][2] field

[1]: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/administrate-field-lazy_has_many/Administrate/Field/LazyHasMany
[2]: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/administrate/Administrate/Field/HasMany
%>

<% if field.data %>
  <% if valid_action?(:show, field.associated_class) %>
    <%= link_to(
      field.display_associated_resource,
      [namespace, field.data],
    ) %>
  <% else %>
    <%= field.display_associated_resource %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>
